name: SpeciesCohabitation
ddl: CREATE TABLE SpeciesCohabitation (SpeciesID INTEGER CHECK (SpeciesID >= 0) NOT NULL, OtherSpeciesID INTEGER CHECK (GroupName != NULL || OtherSpeciesID != NULL), GroupName TEXT CHECK (GroupName != NULL || OtherSpeciesID != NULL), Compatible INTEGER CHECK (Compatible == 0 || Compatible == 1) NOT NULL, UNIQUE (SpeciesID, OtherSpeciesID, GroupName));
